To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Copies of all complaints to the Federal Trade Commission regarding AR Global Investments (https://www.ar-global.com/).

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Alexa Gagosz

communications.subject: Rhode Island Access to Public Records Act Request: Bellevue Capital Partners, LLC
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Rhode Island Access to Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

A copy of all financial documents related to Bellevue Capital Partners, LLC or Bellevue Capital Ventures. These records should include, but are not limited to contracts, purchase orders, invoices, receipts, expense reports, travel authorization requests, vouchers, memos, among other documents. I request such records from Jan. 1, 2020 to present.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Alexa Gagosz

communications.subject: Rhode Island Access to Public Records Act Request: Bellevue Capital emails
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Rhode Island Access to Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

All emails sent between the office and Bellevue Capital Partners LLC or Bellevue Capital Ventures between Nov. 1, 2024 and present. I also request all internal emails sent between office staff that mention "Bellevue Capital Partners" or "Bellevue Capital" or "Bellevue Capital Ventures" from Nov. 1, 2024 to present.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

Alexa Gagosz
